<plot>Haunted by the memories surrounding his partner's death, ex-cop Nick Anderson has fallen into a debilitating downward spiral of depression, anxiety, and an unbearable condition known as achluophobia- a fear of darkness. One stormy night a stranger appears at his door, forcing Nick to confront his deepest fears in order to save the life of someone close to him, as well as his own.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?191388</url></doc>
